        'content' => '<p><span lang="EN-US">As part of the submission process, authors are required to indicate that their submission complies with all the following elements, and accept that submissions that do not comply with these indications may be returned to the author.</span></p><p><strong>1. Declaration of exclusivity and copyright waiver</strong></p><p>The authors have attached the Letter of Exclusivity and Copyright Waiver, in addition to the forms for author and article signed with their personal information (<a href="http://administracion.univalle.edu.co/Documentos/cuadernos/carta_cesion_derechos_de_autor_ingles.doc" target="_blank">download letter in Word format</a>), author form, and article form.</p>',
